    <div class="gem-c-title govuk-!-margin-top-8 govuk-!-margin-bottom-8">
    <p class="gem-c-title__context">
      Policy paper
    </p>
  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    EU (Withdrawal Agreement) Bill
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  

  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">The EU (Withdrawal Agreement) Bill is required to ratify the Withdrawal Agreement, as agreed between the United Kingdom and the European Union, and implement the Agreements (EU, EEA EFTA and Swiss) in domestic law.  This Bill ensures that the United Kingdom is able to fulfil its international obligations, and leave the European Union with a deal.</p>

  </div>
</div>

